      "isDeleted": false,
      "boundElements": [],
      "updated": 1772049362503,
      "link": null,
      "locked": false,
      "text": "get_url(cls, config) -> str\n    returns one big URL with given search parameters\n    \n\n#Internal Use\n_get_param_url(arg, url) -> url\n    returns url if arguments are given\n\n_get_rooms_url(rooms, parser) -> str\n    returns ?filtered rooms?\n\n_concatenate_params_url(...) -> str\n    returns full url",
      "fontSize": 20,
      "fontFamily": 5,
      "textAlign": "left",
      "verticalAlign": "top",
      "containerId": null,
      "originalText": "get_url(cls, config) -> str\n    returns one big URL with given search parameters\n    \n\n#Internal Use\n_get_param_url(arg, url) -> url\n    returns url if arguments are given\n\n_get_rooms_url(rooms, parser) -> str\n    returns ?filtered rooms?\n\n_concatenate_params_url(...) -> str\n    returns full url",
      "autoResize": true,
      "lineHeight": 1.25
    },
