      "link": null,
      "locked": false,
      "text": "get_response(url, config) -> Response\n    handles request errors and request delay\n\nget_content() -> gets content\n\nget_ads_count(content) -> int\n    parses total count of ads from page\n\nget_page_count(content, ads_count, config) -> int\n    page counter\n\nget_ads_on_page(content) -> int\n    page counter\n\nget_ads_urls(home_url, ads_on_page)\n    ???\n\nget_flats_data_on_page(ads_urls, config, flat_parser) -> list[Flats]\n    returns list of flats completely parsed\n\nrun_crawler(config, connector, url, flat_parser)\n    runs crawler that crawls every page",
      "fontSize": 20,
      "fontFamily": 5,
      "textAlign": "left",
      "verticalAlign": "top",
      "containerId": null,
      "originalText": "get_response(url, config) -> Response\n    handles request errors and request delay\n\nget_content() -> gets content\n\nget_ads_count(content) -> int\n    parses total count of ads from page\n\nget_page_count(content, ads_count, config) -> int\n    page counter\n\nget_ads_on_page(content) -> int\n    page counter\n\nget_ads_urls(home_url, ads_on_page)\n    ???\n\nget_flats_data_on_page(ads_urls, config, flat_parser) -> list[Flats]\n    returns list of flats completely parsed\n\nrun_crawler(config, connector, url, flat_parser)\n    runs crawler that crawls every page",
